Required things:
- An iOS device
- Madfut
- proxyman app

If you didn't install proxyman this is the link: https://apps.apple.com/it/app/proxyman-network-debug-tool/id1551292695

How to get the refresh:

- Log out from madfut
- Open proxyman and start it
- Log into madfut with the account from where you want the refresh 
- Stop proxyman 
- search into the proxyman's search bar: oauth2.googleapis.com
- click the one on top that end in /token 
- click reponse
- click view body 
- copy the refresh token 
- enjoy your token
